---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
const title = 'Privacy Policy | classactionsettlementcalc.com';
const description = 'Privacy policy for classactionsettlementcalc.com — how we collect, use, and share visitor data, including the case-review form, Google AdSense, and Google Analytics.';
---
<BaseLayout title={title} description={description}>
  <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
  <p><strong>Last updated:</strong> July 2026.</p>
  <p>Browsing classactionsettlementcalc.com — using the calculator or reading the guides — does not collect any personal information. This policy explains what is collected if you submit our case-review form, what third-party services collect, and what choices you have.</p>

  <h2>Who We Are</h2>
  <p>classactionsettlementcalc.com is operated by The Click Lab Agency LLC (business email: <a href="mailto:hey@theclicklab.agency">hey@theclicklab.agency</a>).</p>

  <h2>Information We Collect</h2>
  <p>The calculator itself requires no account registration and processes all inputs in your browser using JavaScript. No settlement amounts, class size estimates, or claims rate inputs are transmitted to our servers or to any third party.</p>
  <p>If you submit the Class Action case-review form on our homepage, we collect your name, phone number, email address, the case details you enter, and a timestamp of your consent. That information is only collected if you choose to submit the form.</p>
  <p>Beyond the form, data collection occurs only through:</p>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Google AdSense:</strong> Displays advertising. Google collects usage data, device information, and IP address to serve relevant ads, governed by Google&rsquo;s Privacy Policy at <a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">policies.google.com/privacy</a>.</li>
    <li><strong>Google Analytics 4</strong> (property G-E73N9TMNFQ): Aggregate traffic data (page views, session duration, device type). No personally identifiable information is collected.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>How case-review form information is shared</h2>
  <p>If you submit the case-review form, your name, phone number, email address, and case details are shared with one or more attorneys or their agents licensed to practice in your jurisdiction, so they can evaluate your situation and contact you about it. The Click Lab Agency LLC, which operates classactionsettlementcalc.com, is not a law firm, does not provide legal advice, and does not vet, endorse, or guarantee the attorneys in this network. Submitting the form does not create an attorney-client relationship with The Click Lab Agency LLC or with any attorney until and unless that attorney separately agrees to represent you. The Click Lab Agency LLC may be compensated for these referrals.</p>
  <p>By submitting the form, you separately consent to be contacted by phone, text, and email — including by automated dialing technology — by The Click Lab Agency LLC and the attorneys or agents your information is shared with. That consent is not required to use any other part of this site, and you can decline it by not submitting the form.</p>

  <h2>Cookies</h2>
  <p>We do not set first-party cookies beyond what is necessary to record case-review form consent. Opt out of personalized advertising at <a href="https://adssettings.google.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">adssettings.google.com</a>.</p>

  <h2>Data Sharing</h2>
  <p>We do not sell or share visitor data with any third party beyond Google (as described above) and, if you submit the case-review form, the attorneys or agents described above. Anonymous browsing of the calculator and guides is never sold or shared, because it collects no personal information in the first place.</p>

  <h2>Your choices and opt-out</h2>
  <p>The simplest opt-out is not to submit the case-review form. If you have already submitted it and want your information removed or want to withdraw consent to be contacted, email <a href="mailto:hey@theclicklab.agency">hey@theclicklab.agency</a> with the subject line <strong>[OPT-OUT]</strong>, or visit <a href="https://theclicklab.agency/optout" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">theclicklab.agency/optout</a>.</p>

  <h2>California privacy rights (CCPA/CPRA)</h2>
  <p>Sharing case-review form information with attorneys in exchange for compensation may be considered a &ldquo;sale&rdquo; or &ldquo;share&rdquo; of personal information under the California Consumer Privacy Act and its amendments. California residents may opt out of this sharing at any time using either method above. California residents also have the right to know what personal information we hold, to request deletion, and to non-discrimination for exercising these rights — contact us at the email above to make a request.</p>

  <h2>European privacy rights (GDPR)</h2>
  <p>If you are located in the EU/EEA or UK, the legal basis for processing information you submit through the case-review form is your consent, given at the point of submission. You can withdraw that consent at any time using the opt-out methods above; withdrawal does not affect the lawfulness of processing that occurred before withdrawal. Browsing the calculator and guides involves no personal-data processing and requires no legal basis.</p>

  <h2>Children&rsquo;s Privacy</h2>
  <p>This site is not directed at children under 13.</p>

  <h2>Contact</h2>
  <p>Questions? Email <a href="mailto:hey@theclicklab.agency">hey@theclicklab.agency</a>.</p>

  <p>Return to the <a href="/">calculator</a> or see the <a href="/terms/">terms of use</a>.</p>
</BaseLayout>
